  "subject": "[SDNC] Make SDNC Service Mesh compatible",
  "commit_message": "[SDNC] Make SDNC Service Mesh compatible\n\nNormal behavior shouldn't change (https, use of AAF, same\nconfiguration, ...).\n\nChange configuration on DMaaP in order to:\n * Prefer use of (non headless) services\n * Name the port with their protocol\n * allow to disable https (and enable http)\n\nChange-Id: Ie3c12aa7798920a263c7b960d8300fb7734149e4\nIssue-ID: OOM-2258\nSigned-off-by: Sylvain Desbureaux <sylvain.desbureaux@orange.com>\n",
